'''藝術監督'''（{{lang-en|Artistic directors}}）是在藝術組織中擔任執行者的職位，負責管理該組織的相關藝術工作<ref>{{Cite book|title = An Actor Prepares|last = Stanislavski|first = Constantin|publisher = Theatre Arts Inc. New York|year = 1936|isbn = |location = |pages = }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|title = Meyerhold the Director|last = Rudnitsky|first = Konstantin, Transl. G. Petrov|publisher = Ardis, Ann Arbor, MI|year = 1981|isbn = |location = |pages = }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|title = The Empty Space|last = Brook|first = Peter|publisher = Harmondsworth, UK: Pelican|year = 1972|isbn = |location = |pages = }}</ref>。

== 概要 ==
在[[芭蕾舞|芭蕾舞]]中，藝術監督是負責人的職位，必須訓練舞者和節目製作。多數是退休的舞者來擔任，並會發表編舞作品。

